# NM i AI 2026 — Competition Context

## Three independent tasks:

### 1. Astar Island (astar/)
- Predict Norse civilisation terrain after 50-year simulation
- 40x40 map, 6 terrain classes, W×H×6 probability

### 2. Tripletex (tripletex/)
- Task and API specifics: follow official competition materials and Tripletex track instructions during the event.

### 3. NorgesGruppen (norgesgruppen/)
- Task specifics: follow official competition materials and NorgesGruppen track instructions during the event.

## Repo conventions
- Target Python 3.12 for Python code in this repository.
- Persistent project knowledge: read `knowledge/INDEX.md` at session start; load category files only as needed; log issues to `knowledge/ERRORS.md`.
---

## Quick commands
/nmai = Les `knowledge/INDEX.md` ved behov; analyser `tripletex/logs/last_solve.log` (siste run),
implementer i `tripletex/agent.py`, test `python3 tripletex/test_sandbox.py --local-only`,
oppdater `tripletex/data.json` ved eksplisitt scoreboard-/backlog-sync.
